# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout, so Windows
# clones do not introduce CRLF. Taskrail parses Markdown task/state files with
# LF-only delimiters, and shell scripts/Go sources must stay LF cross-platform.
# The parser also tolerates CRLF defensively (internal/taskrail/frontmatter.go),
# but normalized checkout keeps tracked files deterministic everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf
